==English==

===Noun===
'''paint'''

#A substance that is [[apply|applied]] as a [[liquid]] or [[paste]], and dries into a [[solid]] [[coating]] that [[protect]]s or adds [[color]]/[[colour]] to an object or surface to which it has been applied.
#(''in plural'' '''paints''') A set of containers or blocks of paint of different colors/colours, used for painting [[picture]]s.
# {{cattag2|Basketball|Slang}} The [[free-throw lane]].  Always used with ''the''.
#: ''The Nimrods are strong outside, but not very good in the paint.''

