===Verb===
'''to paint''' (''present participle:'' '''painting''', ''past tense and past participe:'' '''painted''')

#''(transitive)'' To apply paint to
#''(transitive)'' To apply (something) in the manner that paint is applied
#''(intransitive)'' To practise the art of painting pictures


